														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1713267">
									

<p>Ayep. We only got ~50% of the stuff we wanted to write done.</p>
<p>Also, people should totally add stuff to the canon! My only requests are that when you put in the hub, 1) Put it something approaching-ish chronological order (so no futuristic sci-fi scenarios right after &quot;Pieces of Mind&quot;) and 2) that you add a quote before your thing. It can be thematically or directly relevant to the story, or it can be only tangentially related.</p>
<p>e: Thanks to Jack Manganese for letting me steal a line from his great piece <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/every-story-someday">Every Story Someday</a>, and to Rumetzen for writing the quote for The End.</p>

							</div>

								
